177 A.3d 125 JPRC, INC. T/A LIQUID ASSETS, PETITIONER-PETITIONER, v. NEW JERSEY DEPARTMENT OF LABOR AND WORKFORCE DEVELOPMENT, RESPONDENT-RESPONDENT.

C-434 September Term 2017

079984 December 13, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

*552A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001736-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
